node.text:
Continuing my photos from my trip with the #ConnectingEurope Express with the @europeancommission . From Lisbon we went to Madrid, continued our way to Bordeaux followed by Italy. We stayed one night in every city.
.
I often woke up for sunrise. When photographing cities it’s great to wake up early and have the streets all to yourself. Plus the light is the best of the day. And sitting in the comfortable train during the day gives enough time to have some rest, do some work, or simply enjoy window views.
.
Cities showed in these series: Milan, Bordeaux, Madrid and Turin
.
#EUYearofRail #traveleurope #DiscoverEU @european_youth_eu @euinnl
.
#italygram #duomomilano #italyisbeautiful #traintravels #citytrips #beautifulbuildings #instabordeaux

node.text:
I just returned from a new adventure: Crossing Europe with the #ConnectingEurope express train. The Connecting Europe Express is an initiative from the @europeancommission to create awareness for train travel in Europe. After all, this year is the #EUYearofRail. Train travel is fast, comfortable and sustainable.
.
What I found very convenient was that the train almost always arrived in the middle of the city. It was very to explore cities right away and just hop on the train to go to the next city. Train travel is the best way to explore all of the different cities in Europe. 
.
I started from Lisbon Portugal finished in Bratislava Slovakia. I visited more than 10 cities in just 9 days. Before hopping on the Connecting Europe Express  I had some time to explore Lisbon. The cute trams in the city caught my eye and I decided to get up early and photograph them with basically no cars in the streets and beautiful soft light. After that we departed from the Estação do Oriente station, which had some really interesting architecture. It was the start of a great adventure, all by train. 
.
#Traveleurope #DiscoverEU @european_youth_eu @euinnl
.
#lisbonlovers #lisbonportugal #traintravels #citytrips #beautifulcity #goldenlight

node.text:
Beautiful streets around Europe. I love exploring and photographing them. This is a collection from streets that I visited during trips in the past. 
.
I just returned home from spending 9 days in the #connectingeurope express train and have many cityscapes and little streets to show you upcoming week. The images in this collection are all from countries the Connecting Europe Express has passed or will still visit: Greece, Italy and the Netherlands.
.
#discoverEU #traveleurope #EUYearofRail #streetsofeurope #europetravel #europetrip #beautifulstreets #beautifultown

node.text:
Today is my last day on the #connectingeurope express train. I've stayed in a different European city every day for 10 days in a row and saw many in between. I loved exploring them all. I also like modern cities, like this collection that has images from Hong Kong, Dubai, Busan and Seoul.
.
Thank you all for following my trip through my stories. I have many images from different cities I have to work in, so you'll see some of that content soon.
.
#traveleurope #discoverEU #moderncities #burjkhalifa #mydubailife #hongkongphotography #cityskyline #amazingcities #skyscraping_architecture

node.text:
I woke up in Madrid, Spain yesterday morning, slept in Bordeaux France last night and arriving in Turin Italy today. I'm traveling by train through Europe with the #connectingeurope express. 
.
Italy is one of my favourite countries in Europe. They just have so much beauty there. I love the little villages along the coast. These photos are from Cinque Terre. The villages of Cinque Terre are connected by train that goes through tunnels in the rocks, making it possible to go from village to village in a very short time.
.
#cinqueterre #loveitaly #italytravel #italygram #ig_italia #italytrip #coastalliving #beautifultown #beautifulvillage #italy_vacations #cinqueterreitaly #traveleurope #discovereu

node.text:
While I'm sitting on the #connectingeurope express train this week and looking out of the window dreaming away from all the different landscapes I see passing by, the first little mushrooms are already popping out of the ground when the forests are wet. With September just started the first signs of autumn can already be seen in some parts of Europe.
.
#discovereu #mushrooms_of_our_world #mushroomspotting #mushroomseason #macrophotography #macroworld #macro_kings #macronature #macramelove

node.text:
The upcoming days I am crossing Europe by train with the #connectingeuropeexpress . This year is the Year of Rail. Using train travel is comfortable and sustainable. The CEE crosses 26 countries in 36 days. I will be in different countries and cities almost every day. It also crosses my hometown Amsterdam, to be seen in this collection. Follow my stories in the upcoming 9 days to see where the trains will take me. I'll also explain how easy it is to travel by train through Europe, how to find the nice spots, how to plan and much more :)
.
#euyearofrail #traveleurope #discovereu #disovereurope #traintravel #amsterdamcity #amsterdamview #amsterdamvibe #livinginamsterdam #visitamsterdam #amsterdamworld #sonyalpha
